high_descs: Walk down the hallway and enter the last room on the right and walk to the desk.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn towards the plate.
Stab the plate on the bed.
Pick up the white plate with the knife.
Turn around, exit room, walk to the next room on the right and enter it, walk to the sink.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the Knife and Plate from the bedroom to the SinkBasin in the bathroom.

high_descs: Turn left and walk a few feet forward then left into the bedroom with a wood desk.
Pick up the knife nearest the lamp from the table.
Turn left and face towards the plate on the bed.
Put the knife down on the plate on the bed.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the bed.
Leave the bedroom and turn right, then turn right into the sink.
Put the plate with knife down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Knife on Plate in the SinkBasin

high_descs: Turn left. Turn left, get to the desk. Go forward to the door. Turn right. Go inside and then turn right. Reach the shelf. Turn left. Move to the bed. Turn to the right.
Grab the knife.
Turn around, turn right.
Place the knife on the plate.
Grab the plate and knife.
Turn around. Reach the sink. Turn right. Reach the door, turn left. Reach the sink. Turn left. After the sink, turn left. Enter the bathroom, turn left. Turn right, turn right again.
Place the plate with the knife on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Find a Knife and a Plate. Place them on the SinkBasin.
